author: Ildefonso Ortiz
title: Mexico Sees 22 Percent Spike in Coronavirus Deaths in One Day
description: Health officials in Mexico saw a 22 percent spike in fatalities related to the novel Coronavirus (COVID-19). In one day, the number rose by 74 for a total of 406 deceased since the pandemic arrived.
content:
Health officials in Mexico saw a 22 percent spike in fatalities related to the novel Coronavirus (COVID-19). In one day, the number rose by 74 for a total of 406 deceased since the pandemic arrived.
